# 컴포넌트 템플릿 — LG CHO Portal

Y26_HR 코드베이스의 실제 컴포넌트. 복사 후 콘텐츠만 교체한다.

---

## 목차
1. [HTML 문서 셸](#1-html-문서-셸)
2. [Top Bar](#2-top-bar)
3. [Hero 섹션](#3-hero-섹션)
4. [Menu Card (Hub용)](#4-menu-card-hub용)
5. [Stats Row](#5-stats-row)
6. [Principle Card (Do/Don't)](#6-principle-card-dodont)
7. [VIBE Category 2-column](#7-vibe-category-2-column)
8. [Phase Tab Navigation](#8-phase-tab-navigation)
9. [Matrix Table](#9-matrix-table)
10. [Modal](#10-modal)
11. [Footer](#11-footer)

---

## 1. HTML 문서 셸

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>[페이지 제목]</title>
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+KR:wght@300;400;500;700;900&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.1/css/all.min.css">
<style>
:root {
  --red:#A50034; --red-mid:#c4003d; --red-light:#f9e6ec;
  --dark:#1a1a1a; --g900:#222; --g700:#4b4b4d; --g500:#787a7d; --g300:#c8c8c8; --g100:#f4f4f4; --white:#fff;
  --yellow:#FBBF24;
  --text-dark:#1F2937; --bg-light:#F3F4F6;
  --font:'Noto Sans KR',system-ui,sans-serif;
}
*{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{font-family:var(--font);background:[#1a1a1a OR #F9FAFB];color:[var(--white) OR #1F2937];line-height:1.65}
/* 컴포넌트별 스타일 추가 */
</style>
</head>
<body>
<!-- TOP BAR -->
<!-- HERO -->
<!-- MAIN CONTENT -->
<!-- FOOTER (선택) -->
</body>
</html>
```

---

## 2. Top Bar

```html
<!-- TOP BAR -->
<div class="top-bar">
  <div class="tb-left">
    <div class="lg-logo">LG</div>
